OL,3,CWhen could Andy Burnham become the
OL,4,Cprime minister?
OL,6,FBy Emily Youlton, Senior Politics
OL,7,FProducer
OL,9,FLabour's ruling body, the National
OL,10,FExecutive Committee (NEC), has
OL,11,Freleased a timetable for the election
OL,12,Fof a new party leader, which could
OL,13,Fmean a new prime minister is in place
OL,14,Fas early as next month.
OL,16,FSir Keir Starmer resigned on Monday
OL,17,Fafter mounting pressure to step down
OL,18,Ffollowing Labour's disastrous wipeout
OL,19,Fat the local elections in May.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
