OL,3,CWhen could Andy Burnham become the
OL,4,Cprime minister?
OL,6,FThen, Andy Burnham returned to
OL,7,FWestminster as an MP after winning
OL,8,Fmore than half of the votes at the
OL,9,FMakerfield by-election and announced
OL,10,Fhis intention to stand as leader.
OL,12,FCurrently, Burnham is the only person
OL,13,Fwho has said he will stand for
OL,14,Fleadership after former Health
OL,15,FSecretary Wes Streeting backed the
OL,16,Fformer Manchester Mayor on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
