OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782521274
OL,3,CWhen could Andy Burnham become the
OL,4,Cprime minister?
OL,6,FCabinet minister Darren Jones was
OL,7,Frumoured to be standing after Starmer
OL,8,Floyalists pushed for a contest, but he
OL,9,Fruled himself out and backed Burnham
OL,10,Fon Wednesday.
OL,12,FThe former Armed Forces Minister, Al
OL,13,FCarns is refusing to rule out standing
OL,14,Fagainst Burnham and has continued
OL,15,Fposting about a five-point plan for
OL,16,Fthe UK on social media.
OL,18,FSo, how quickly will the UK get a new
OL,19,Fleader of the Labour Party and
OL,20,Ftherefore a new prime minister? ITV
OL,21,FNews explains.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
