OL,3,CWhen could Andy Burnham become the
OL,4,Cprime minister?
OL,6,FNomination period
OL,8,FParliamentary Labour Party (PLP)
OL,9,Fnominations will open on July 9, and
OL,10,Fclose on July 15.
OL,12,FThe PLP consists of all Labour MPs,
OL,13,Fand each candidate needs at least 20%
OL,14,Fof this group to support them to stand
OL,15,Fin a leadership contest, which is 81
OL,16,FMPs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
