OL,3,CWhen could Andy Burnham become the
OL,4,Cprime minister?
OL,6,FTechnically, this can allow up to five
OL,7,Fcandidates to be on the ballot, but
OL,8,FBurnham likely has much more than the
OL,9,Frequired numbers, so there will be
OL,10,Ffewer candidates, if any.
OL,12,FOnce PLP nominations close, so-called
OL,13,F"affiliate nominations" open for 24
OL,14,Fhours between July 15 and July 16 -
OL,15,Fthis is for groups like trade unions
OL,16,Fand organisations linked with Labour.
OL,18,FThose standing must also receive
OL,19,Fbacking from at least three
OL,20,Faffiliates, two of which must be trade
OL,21,Funions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
