OL,3,CWhen could Andy Burnham become the
OL,4,Cprime minister?
OL,6,FThere's another option where the
OL,7,Fcandidate can instead garner support
OL,8,Ffrom 5% of Constituency Labour Party
OL,9,F(CLP) groups, essentially the local
OL,10,FLabour teams.
OL,12,FBut with Burnham, it is generally
OL,13,Fassumed he has the unions on his side,
OL,14,Fso it's looking unlikely this will be
OL,15,Fneeded.
OL,17,FVoting or a Coronation
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
