OL,3,CWhen could Andy Burnham become the
OL,4,Cprime minister?
OL,6,FThe NEC has said that if there is only
OL,7,Fone candidate and they are "validly
OL,8,Fnominated" - meaning they have more
OL,9,Fthan the 81 MPs and the unions onside
OL,10,F- then a new leader will be announced
OL,11,Fon July 17.
OL,13,FThis will be done via a special
OL,14,Fconference and means that if Burnham
OL,15,Fis the only candidate, he could be the
OL,16,Fleader and therefore the prime
OL,17,Fminister that same day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
