OL,3,CWhen could Andy Burnham become the
OL,4,Cprime minister?
OL,6,FIf someone else throws their hat in
OL,7,Fthe ring and garners the support from
OL,8,Fwithin the party, then it would go to
OL,9,Fa vote.
OL,11,FThe voting would be before members of
OL,12,Fthe Labour party who have registered
OL,13,Fbefore December 25, 2025, and would
OL,14,Frun from August 6 to August 27.
OL,16,FIt will be a single-round preferential
OL,17,Fvoting system, where if one candidate
OL,18,Freceives more than 50% of the vote in
OL,19,Fthe first round, they automatically
OL,20,Fwin.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
