OL,3,CWhen could Andy Burnham become the
OL,4,Cprime minister?
OL,6,FIf they do not, then the preferences
OL,7,Fare counted until a candidate reaches
OL,8,Fthe 50% threshold.
OL,10,FA winner would then be announced at a
OL,11,Fspecial conference on August 29, but
OL,12,Fit is looking increasingly unlikely.
