OL,3,CWhen could Andy Burnham become the
OL,4,Cprime minister?
OL,6,FBurnham is yet to announce any formal
OL,7,Fpolicy plans if he becomes prime
OL,8,Fminister, but is due to give a speech
OL,9,Fsetting out his vision for the economy
OL,10,Fin Manchester on Monday.
OL,12,FSome MPs are concerned that they do
OL,13,Fnot know what Burnham stands for and
OL,14,Fwant a contest to ensure his ideas are
OL,15,Ftested.
OL,17,FEven if there is no contest, the NEC
OL,18,Fstates that there will be a husting
OL,19,Ffor MPs on July 13, where they can
OL,20,Fquestion candidates on their plans for
OL,21,Fthe party and country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
